            <p>Hello! I'm <strong>Alex Johnson</strong>, a web developer, designer, and technology enthusiast. With a passion for all things digital, I specialize in creating interactive, responsive, and user-focused websites that not only look great but also perform exceptionally well. My journey into web development started over five years ago, and since then, I've helped individuals and businesses across various industries create their digital presence.</p>

