            <p>I began my professional career as a graphic designer, creating branding and visual identities for startups. Over time, I became fascinated by the technical side of things—how design can be brought to life on the web. That’s when I made the transition into web development. I studied web technologies and honed my skills by working on personal projects and taking on freelance gigs. Today, I blend both design and development to create unique digital experiences.</p>

