                <li><strong>SEO Optimization:</strong> Implementing best practices to help websites rank higher in search engines</li>
                <li><strong>CMS Platforms:</strong> WordPress, Webflow</li>
            </ul>

            <h3>Work Philosophy</h3>
            <p>For me, web development is more than just writing code. It’s about solving problems and creating seamless user experiences. I focus on clean, modular code that’s easy to maintain and scale. I also believe that collaboration is key—I enjoy working closely with my clients to understand their vision and objectives, ensuring that the final product exceeds expectations.</p>

            <h3>Outside of Work</h3>
            <p>When I'm not coding or designing, I enjoy staying active and exploring the outdoors. On weekends, you’ll often find me hiking the trails around the Bay Area or enjoying a good game of basketball with friends. I’m also a bit of a coffee connoisseur and love discovering new coffee shops.</p>

